:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/07\/way-of-moderation\/","url_meta":{"origin":34839,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Balance: You must take the way of moderation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 7, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Buraydah al-Aslami reported: I went out one day to fulfill a need, and there was the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, walking before me. The Prophet took my hand, and we set out walking together. A man was praying before us who was performing many bowings and prostrations.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38549,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/12\/25\/tahajjud-awf\/","url_meta":{"origin":34839,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Tahajjud: Awf witnesses the Prophet\u2019s night prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 25, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Awf ibn Malik reported: I stood with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, to pray at night. The Prophet began to recite Surat al-Baqarah and he would not pass by a verse of mercy but that he would ask for it, nor did he pass by\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33950,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/01\/27\/five-deeds-to-enter-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34839,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jannah: Five deeds for the faithful to enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 27, 202